535
01:08:33,943 --> 01:08:36,433
But he's only five!

536
01:08:42,085 --> 01:08:45,335
Sleep well, little children.

537
01:08:58,801 --> 01:08:59,791
Sosuke!

538
01:09:01,404 --> 01:09:02,484
Sosuke!

539
01:09:03,872 --> 01:09:05,303
Ow!

540
01:09:08,111 --> 01:09:09,571
Good morning, Ponyo.

541
01:09:10,145 --> 01:09:12,225
Morning, Sosuke.

542
01:09:18,755 --> 01:09:21,005
We almost got flooded.

543
01:09:44,747 --> 01:09:48,287
- Where's Lisa?
- She must be stuck someplace.

544
01:09:48,917 --> 01:09:51,407
I wish we had a boat.

545
01:09:54,924 --> 01:09:56,264
There's a boat!

546
01:09:58,661 --> 01:09:59,711
We can't fit.

