01:11:44,133 --> 01:11:45,003
Shipshape?

565
01:11:45,268 --> 01:11:45,908
Shipshape!

566
01:11:46,269 --> 01:11:48,609
Shipshape! Shipshape!

567
01:12:12,028 --> 01:12:13,018
Is it hot?

568
01:12:13,296 --> 01:12:14,406
Hot!

569
01:12:19,302 --> 01:12:20,822
It's hot.

570
01:12:24,006 --> 01:12:26,316
- The candle's burning.
- It's burning!

571
01:12:26,909 --> 01:12:29,898
Hot hot hot!

572
01:12:37,920 --> 01:12:39,560
It's hot.

573
01:12:50,700 --> 01:12:51,840
Awesome!

574
01:12:53,836 --> 01:12:56,326
We're shipshape, Sosuke!

575
01:12:56,939 --> 01:12:58,519
This is great.

576
01:13:06,115 --> 01:13:07,955
This is so much fun.

577
01:13:09,485 --> 01:13:11,764
It's burning, Sosuke.

578
01:13:12,555 --> 01:13:14,425
It's really hot.

579
01:13:15,424 --> 01:13:18,734
