580
01:13:19,729 --> 01:13:21,189
Okay, I'm the lookout.

581
01:13:48,457 --> 01:13:49,797
There's a road.

582
01:13:50,126 --> 01:13:51,876
That's the road Lisa took.

583
01:13:54,664 --> 01:13:56,063
I don't see her.

584
01:13:56,632 --> 01:13:59,652
You will.
She gave me her promise.

585
01:14:04,840 --> 01:14:07,680
Ancient fish...
from the Devonian age!

586
01:14:08,210 --> 01:14:10,050
There's Bothriolepis.

587
01:14:15,451 --> 01:14:16,381
That one is...

588
01:14:16,786 --> 01:14:17,636
Dipnorhynchus.

589
01:14:17,954 --> 01:14:19,244
Dipnorhynchus!

590
01:14:19,622 --> 01:14:21,612
That one's really huge.

591
01:14:22,158 --> 01:14:23,648
That's Devonynchus.

592
01:14:24,060 --> 01:14:25,960
Devonynchus!

593
01:14:32,568 --> 01:14:34,558
Ahoy!

594
01:14:38,140 --> 01:14:38,990
A boat!

595
01:14:40,242 --> 01:14:41,642
Ahoy!

596
01:14:43,145 --> 01:14:44,635
