597
01:14:46,048 --> 01:14:47,628
Ahoy!

598
01:14:49,719 --> 01:14:50,829
Ow!

599
01:14:58,160 --> 01:14:59,330
Pretty good, huh?

600
01:15:03,265 --> 01:15:04,665
Now, Ponyo.

601
01:15:11,140 --> 01:15:12,950
Hello.

602
01:15:13,409 --> 01:15:15,749
That's a wonderful
boat you have.

603
01:15:16,278 --> 01:15:18,908
Why, you're Lisa's little boy.

604
01:15:19,582 --> 01:15:21,772
He's not little. he's Sosuke.
a

