- Hold on a second.

638
01:18:16,025 --> 01:18:16,875
Milk!

639
01:18:17,993 --> 01:18:19,223
Oh my...

640
01:18:20,429 --> 01:18:21,359
Milk!

641
01:18:21,630 --> 01:18:23,820
She ate up all the ham.

642
01:18:24,266 --> 01:18:26,816
This will help me
make good milk.

643
01:18:27,403 --> 01:18:31,033
Can you use another candle
for your boat, Sosuke?

644
01:18:31,674 --> 01:18:34,604
Thanks.
Ponyo will make it bigger.

645
01:18:35,978 --> 01:18:36,908
Be careful!

646
01:18:37,179 --> 01:18:38,609
Thank you both!

647
01:18:44,787 --> 01:18:46,157
What is it, dear?

648
01:18:50,893 --> 01:18:52,233
Don't cry.

649
01:19:11,513 --> 01:19:12,913
Ponyo!

650
01:19:25,894 --> 01:19:27,204
Sosuke!

651
01:19:29,365 --> 01:19:31,885
Where's Lisa?
Isn't she with you?

652
01:19:32,501 --> 01:19:35,311
I'm going to pick her up.

653
01:19:35,971 --> 01:19:38,931
So she survived that wave?

654
01:19:39,808 --> 01:19:42,118
Sosuke, take me with you!

655
01:19:42,845 --> 01:19:45,215
Later, Kumiko.
I'm busy now.

656
01:19:45,814 --> 01:19:48,804
Everyone from the center
evacuated to the park.

657
01:19:49,418 --> 01:19:51,348
- Keep safe!
- You can do it!

658
01:19:52,087 --> 01:19:55,307
We'll send a boat
for them later.

659
01:19:55,991 --> 01:19:57,951
Good luck, captain!

660
01:20:47,276 --> 01:20:49,796
Time for a new candle, Ponyo.

661
01:20:53,982 --> 01:20:56,762
We're okay.
I have another one.

662
01:20:57,920 --> 01:21:00,530
Ow! It's still pretty hot.

663
01:21:05,994 --> 01:21:08,334
Bye-bye.

664
01:21:09,465 --> 01:21:12,425
Can you make this candle bigger?

665
01:21:13,035 --> 01:21:14,325
All right.

666
01:21:20,042 --> 01:21:22,562
Are you sleepy, Ponyo?

667
01:21:30,085 --> 01:21:31,165
Ponyo!

668
01:21:47,269 --> 01:21:48,729
Ponyo! Ponyo!

669
01:22:46,862 --> 01:22:49,032
Good...it's shallow enough to walk.

670
01:23:15,824 --> 01:23:17,114
A road!

671
01:23:29,972 --> 01:23:31,081
It's shrinking!

672
01:23:32,908 --> 01:23:34,138
Ponyo!

673
01:23:56,131 --> 01:23:57,911
Ponyo, wake up!

674
01:24:00,836 --> 01:24:02,386
Sosuke...

675
01:24:08,510 --> 01:24:09,820
Don't scare me.

676
01:24:10,212 --> 01:24:12,902
I thought you were
turning into a fish.

677
01:24:25,527 --> 01:24:26,397
Lisa's car!

678
01:24:26,929 --> 01:24:28,829
Ponyo, that's her car!

679
01:24:33,001 --> 01:24:34,581
Lisa!

680
01:24:38,173 --> 01:24:38,992
Lisa!

681
01:24:43,111 --> 01:24:44,631
Lisa!

682
01:24:47,015 --> 01:24:48,535
Lisa!

