01:24:57,192 --> 01:24:59,092
Lisa!

684
01:25:02,030 --> 01:25:03,429
Lisa!

685
01:25:32,127 --> 01:25:34,147
Here's your boat.

686
01:25:34,596 --> 01:25:37,175
Your eyes are wet.

687
01:25:44,239 --> 01:25:45,968
Let's find Lisa.

688
01:26:33,488 --> 01:26:36,008
- You forgot your wrap!
- Who needs it?

689
01:26:36,491 --> 01:26:38,681
Look. it's a whale!
a

690
01:26:39,995 --> 01:26:44,825
- My knees don't hurt anymore!
- What were we so afraid of?

691
01:26:45,634 --> 01:26:48,624
- Is this the Other Side?
- Who cares? It's wonderful.

692
01:26:51,406 --> 01:26:54,096
Attention, please!
Gather round.

693
01:26:54,776 --> 01:26:55,916
Coming!

694
01:26:56,211 --> 01:26:57,671
Shall we?

695
01:27:00,115 --> 01:27:01,865
It's so nice to run.

696
01:27:02,384 --> 01:27:04,054
Meet you there!

697
01:27:07,456 --> 01:27:09,156
The winner!

698
01:27:11,460 --> 01:27:13,450
You're so fast, Kayo.

699
01:27:14,496 --> 01:27:15,986
Quiet, everyone!

700
01:27:17,065 --> 01:27:19,054
The moment
of truth is at hand.

701
01:27:19,568 --> 01:27:21,738
Sosuke and Ponyo
are almost here.

702
01:27:22,170 --> 01:27:23,430
It's so romantic.

703
01:27:23,739 --> 01:27:27,428
- Will love triumph?
- I'm so excited!

704
01:27:29,377 --> 01:27:30,457
Quiet!

705
01:27:30,746 --> 01:27:35,316
Very soon, you will bear witness
to a sacred trial of love.

706
01:27:37,319 --> 01:27:41,189
Mr. Fujimoto, you're not
up to something, are you?

707
01:27:41,923 --> 01:27:44,532
Nonsense, he's her father.

708
01:27:45,093 --> 01:27:48,843
They'll be fine...
if she doesn't wake up.

709
01:27:49,531 --> 01:27:51,021
Now excuse me!

710
01:27:59,541 --> 01:28:01,561
I'd like to believe him...

711
01:28:01,977 --> 01:28:04,117
Where's Lisa gone to?

712
01:28:04,579 --> 01:28:08,739
She's been talking with
Ponyo's mother for ages.

713
01:28:17,359 --> 01:28:19,609
l hope she's okay.

714
01:28:20,061 --> 01:28:22,340
What are they talking about?

715
01:28:22,798 --> 01:28:25,138
Let's find out. Lisa!

716
01:28:25,600 --> 01:28:28,440
Lisa!

717
01:28:34,409 --> 01:28:40,529
We're all rooting
for Sosuke and Ponyo!

718
01:28:54,696 --> 01:28:55,746
Lisa!

719
01:28:56,031 --> 01:28:59,101
- You must be worried.
- Sosuke will be just fine.

720
01:28:59,668 --> 01:29:01,978
He's a strong little boy.

721
01:29:03,271 --> 01:29:06,431
Thanks, everyone.
He'll need your support.

722
01:29:15,584 --> 01:29:17,313
Ponyo, it's a tunnel.

723
01:29:25,727 --> 01:29:28,217
“STOP”

724
01:29:33,168 --> 01:29:35,067
I've been here before.

725
01:29:36,438 --> 01:29:37,428
Ponyo?

726
01:29:37,973 --> 01:29:39,673
I don't like this place.

727
01:29:44,079 --> 01:29:45,858
Don't let go of my hand.

728
01:30:24,085 --> 01:30:25,255
Ponyo!

729
01:30:44,572 --> 01:30:45,422
Ponyo!

730
01:30:53,915 --> 01:30:54,765
Ponyo!

731
01:31:16,838 --> 01:31:18,858
Please don't die!

732
01:31:19,574 --> 01:31:21,063
Ponyo!

733
01:31:22,077 --> 01:31:24,247
Wake up, Ponyo!

734
01:31:24,679 --> 01:31:26,959
Let her sleep.

735
01:31:28,350 --> 01:31:30,080
I've been waiting for you, Sosuke.

736
01:31:30,452 --> 01:31:33,382
Lisa and the old ladies
are waiting too.

737
01:31:34,756 --> 01:31:35,656
Lisa?!

738
01:31:35,991 --> 01:31:39,011
Won't you come with me?
You and Ponyo.

739
01:31:42,197 --> 01:31:44,597
Let's not wake her.

740
01:31:45,066 --> 01:31:46,965
Sosuke!

741
01:31:47,602 --> 01:31:50,152
Don't listen to him!

742
01:31:51,106 --> 01:31:53,976
He tricked everyone
into going with him.

743
01:31:54,509 --> 01:31:55,209
Toki!

744
01:31:55,443 --> 01:31:57,143
But he couldn't fool me!

745
01:31:58,179 --> 01:32:03,039
There's no time, I tell you.
Don't you see what's happening?

746
01:32:03,852 --> 01:32:06,952
If the Moon comes
any closer, we're finished!

747
01:32:07,756 --> 01:32:10,416
Is that the best
you can do?

748
01:32:11,259 --> 01:32:13,369
Sosuke, come here!

749
01:32:13,862 --> 01:32:16,882
Listen to me. Sosuke.
a
