750
01:32:17,432 --> 01:32:19,132
Don't make me use force.

751
01:32:20,835 --> 01:32:21,855
Ponyo!

752
01:32:23,571 --> 01:32:25,881
Is this how you
treat your father?

753
01:32:33,048 --> 01:32:34,157
Ponyo!

754
01:32:34,449 --> 01:32:36,728
Run, Sosuke!

755
01:32:37,185 --> 01:32:39,145
You don't understand!

756
01:32:44,492 --> 01:32:45,952
You can make it!

757
01:32:48,263 --> 01:32:49,492
Jump!

758
01:33:28,970 --> 01:33:30,110
Now what?

759
01:34:25,193 --> 01:34:26,013
Lisa!

760
01:34:26,261 --> 01:34:27,311
Sosuke!

761
01:34:27,695 --> 01:34:28,715
Ponyo!

762
01:34:33,902 --> 01:34:37,002
- Look over there.
- Where are we?

763
01:34:47,815 --> 01:34:49,684
So, you are Sosuke.

764
01:34:50,151 --> 01:34:53,081
Hello. Are you
Ponyo's mother?

765
01:34:53,755 --> 01:34:54,575
Yes.

766
01:34:55,190 --> 01:34:59,139
I want to thank you for bringing
my daughter back to me.

767
01:35:00,328 --> 01:35:05,128
Ponyo wanted to be like you,
but she unleashed a terrible power.

768
01:35:06,868 --> 01:35:10,268
To become human, she must be loved...

769
01:35:10,872 --> 01:35:13,452
..for who she really is.

770
01:35:14,309 --> 01:35:17,879
Do you know that Ponyo was a fish?

771
01:35:18,613 --> 01:35:19,463
Yes.

772
01:35:19,714 --> 01:35:23,193
Your blood made her human...almost.

773
01:35:23,818 --> 01:35:24,668
That's right!

774
01:35:24,919 --> 01:35:27,959
Ponyo licked
my cut and made it better.

775
01:35:28,523 --> 01:35:30,633
So that's why she changed!

776
01:35:32,026 --> 01:35:35,246
Can you accept her as she is?

777
01:35:36,030 --> 01:35:37,840
I'll always love Ponyo...

778
01:35:38,266 --> 01:35:40,486
...whether she's a fish. a human...
a

779
01:35:40,935 --> 01:35:43,045
..or in between.

780
01:35:56,684 --> 01:35:58,764
Come, Ponyo.

781
01:36:13,334 --> 01:36:17,554
Sosuke has promised
to accept you as you are.

782
01:36:20,975 --> 01:36:24,195
But first, you must
.
give up your powers.

783
01:36:25,179 --> 01:36:26,639
Can you do that?

784
01:36:37,058 --> 01:36:40,308
Kiss this bubble
when you return to land...

785
01:36:40,895 --> 01:36:44,735
..and Ponyo
will be a little girl.

786
01:36:48,069 --> 01:36:50,089
Way to go, Ponyo!

787
01:36:51,072 --> 01:36:53,412
Thank you, Ponyo’s mother!

788
01:36:59,580 --> 01:37:02,740
Now the planet is safe again.

789
01:37:06,354 --> 01:37:08,194
Splendid, Sosuke!

790
01:37:14,662 --> 01:37:16,152
Sosuke!

791
01:37:40,288 --> 01:37:41,897
I'm grateful, Lisa.

792
01:37:42,523 --> 01:37:44,863
Thank you, Gran Mamare.

793
01:37:56,604 --> 01:37:59,474
There you are!
Are you all right?

794
01:38:04,846 --> 01:38:06,575
Wait, I'll get the wheelchairs.

795
01:38:06,948 --> 01:38:08,848
Don't bother, we'll walk.

796
01:38:09,250 --> 01:38:11,390
It's all so exciting.

797
01:38:14,956 --> 01:38:16,476
I believe this is yours.

798
01:38:19,227 --> 01:38:20,077
Thanks.

799
01:38:20,762 --> 01:38:24,222
I hope you'll
forgive me...may I?

800
01:38:30,438 --> 01:38:32,248
Take good care of her.

801
01:38:34,809 --> 01:38:36,479
It's Koichi!

802
01:38:40,915 --> 01:38:42,725
Koichi!

803
01:38:46,487 --> 01:38:49,447
It's Lisa!
And there's Sosuke!

804
01:38:52,193 --> 01:38:54,943
Look, Ponyo.
It's Koichi!

